Name: Air Gun Fighter
About the game: Nato armies are engaged in a 21th century conflict against Russian Federation Army. As a Top Gun Pilot from US Air Force, you fly the best American Fighters (F18, F35, F22...) throught multiple missions across battlefields around the world (Cuba, Lebanon, Ukraine...) in cooperation with your European Allies Aircrafts (Typhoon, Rafale, Mirage...). You will be engaged in air combat againsts Russian Fighters (Mig 27, Mig 33, Su 37...). Lock your targets, choose amongst different missile systems and riffle, shoot and forget! Powered by an very realistic physic engine that makes the game highly playable, Air Gun Fighter will make you feel real sensations of modern air combat.
